---
title: Carb Smart Bacon and Veggie Fritters with Apple and Goat Cheese Salad
description: These fritters are pan-fried with bacon to bring delicious, salty flavour to humble grated veggies. The pretty plate is made complete with an apple and goat cheese salad for a boost of wholesome goodness!

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
